// File: internal/api/routes.http

### Health check
GET http://localhost:8080/health

### Create a new CA
POST http://localhost:8080/ca
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "server_name": "vpn-europe",
  "valid_years": 3
}

### Issue server certificate
POST http://localhost:8080/server-cert
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "server_name": "vpn-europe"
}

### Issue client certificate
POST http://localhost:8080/client-cert
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "server_name": "vpn-europe",
  "common_name": "client-test-01"
}

### Get full server OpenVPN config
GET http://localhost:8080/ovpn/server-config/vpn-europe

### Get full client OpenVPN config
GET http://localhost:8080/ovpn/client-config/client-test-01